{"tid":1639373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係時候收美心皮！！！","createTime":"2019-10-08T15:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T09:46:32.000Z","uid":270153,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"10597fccd2d475a48e2a858902e29024a696b141","tid":1639373,"uid":270153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:08:46.000Z","msg":"請受小弟<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">道歉</span></span>🙇🏻連登新手，啱啱做咗標題撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">sorry sorry sorry</span>😫<br />\n<br />\n想搞大個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">坐爆Starbucks, 元氣</span></span>活動，睇睇大家有乜意見！<br />\n活動名稱（有咁好請出聲）:<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">&ldquo;<span style=\"color: orange;\">和理 hea</span>&quot;</span></span><br />\n<br />\n活動目的: <br />\n1)&quot;<span style=\"color: orange;\">和理 hea</span>&quot; <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">坐 Starbucks 免費飲水</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">元氣免費飲綠茶食薑</span></span>，坐下嘆冷氣！（係咪好撚簡單呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n2)瞄準美心，繁忙時間<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打擊生意</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3)强烈呼籲Starbucks, 元氣<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">取消美心特許經營權</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n適合人仕: <span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>和理非</strong></span></span>、學生、OL<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">和理hea</span>於<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">繁忙時間</span></span>，鼓勵慢慢落單改單問長問短，務求排隊趕客、<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">連外買都買唔到!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日期時間: （日子時間大家討論，肯做的話<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">日日都做</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n週日星期二、四繁忙時間  午飯12-2pm、晚飯7-9pm <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">完全迫爆佢</span></strong></span> <br />\n週末星期六、日 全日 未能出席活動嘅和理非同我<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>迫爆佢</strong></span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n活動地點: <br />\n1)美心特許經營 <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">Starbucks 星巴克咖啡</span></span></strong>, <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">元氣壽司</span></span></strong><br />\n2)美心集團<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">MX</span></strong>, <strong><span style=\"color: green;\">香港地</span></strong>, <strong><span style=\"color: green;\">can.teen</span></strong>等<br />\n<br />\n活動原因:<br />\n美心創始人女兒伍淑清到聯合國<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">抹黑香港運動為 &quot;騷亂&quot;</span></span></strong>，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">支持香港政府及警察</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">幫襯</span></strong></span>就梗係要去<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃絲啦</span></strong></span>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n慢慢坐，做吓嘢，hea吓就梗係去Starbucks丶元氣飲杯水，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">慢慢hea</span></strong></span>！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和理非，用10分鐘食完個晏晝，之後去飲杯水坐下打機啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢件事講就講咗好耐，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">未見過正式做得爆</span></strong></span>！就係呢幾日內同我推爆佢做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">想美心清盤就做嘢啦屌！</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb7c3d60538d123b9a512837a813b26d801210be","tid":1639373,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a10f6e557f428c9509cc7656b50b77fee620a8b","tid":1639373,"uid":141270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:11:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f506ff8a8747b2c028b23c8560c01d42f8bd04e9","tid":1639373,"uid":162614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:12:38.000Z","msg":"下午茶anyone join"},{"pid":"e1f75c613452382bc4930d2ef4efce8a204ba9a0","tid":1639373,"uid":8230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:14:18.000Z","msg":"和你hea！返完全日工緊係去starbucks、元氣抖下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9d1f6bd5231d3dc9d060be59c9bdc9cb924260","tid":1639373,"uid":86699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:14:37.000Z","msg":"嗱，日日都去坐and 吹下水，返工嘅員工又唔使咁多嘢做，輕輕鬆鬆又一日，真係唔錯㗎！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0eeugdT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0eeugdT.jpg&h=31e84e15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f8106b3bd5990b97288a8a42cfb85afd2d7cd2f","tid":1639373,"uid":270153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1f75c613452382bc4930d2ef4efce8a204ba9a0","tid":1639373,"uid":8230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T15:14:18.000Z","msg":"和你hea！返完全日工緊係去starbucks、元氣抖下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10